/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a car on the road, giving a driver's eye view of the scene. The street is flanked by lush green trees and bushes, adding a touch of nature to the urban landscape. Power lines crisscross above, forming a network against the clear blue sky. Buildings of various sizes and designs line the street, their facades reflecting the architectural diversity of the city. The sun shines brightly in the top right corner of the image, casting a warm glow over the scene.
